<br>
Nigeria. Forty dollars American tucked into your passport gets you onto the street free and clear, I know this for certain. There are plenty of 3rd world toilets that won't care if you have a visa or not. A surprising number of those toilets are in this hemisphere, and yes, you can walk to them.<br>
<br>
<br>
Physically, an 18-year old is very much an adult. I think the issue that distresses you is that the average American 18-year old behaves like a pre-schooler.<br>
<br>
This has nothing to do with biology, and everything to do with society. We treat them as children, and they stay children, far past the point at which they should become responsible people. Parents indulge their children to the point of excess, and the result is that many of the children refuse to grow up before the age of 35.<br>
<br>
While our people are physically mature at the age of 18, they are behaviorally retarded. Retarded, as in the technical definition.<br>
<br>
