In 1099, the armies of the First Crusade ... captured Jerusalem and were popularly reported as wading in the blood of their slain Muslim foes ... In 1187, the Muslim jihad, or holy war ... was called for.  Over the weekend President George Bush described his war on terrorism as a &quot;new crusade''.<br>
